which is slower but simpler and harder to corrupt.\n\nSo: no global blow-up, but yes, one huge session can make capture slower over time. For this POC, I’d keep it unless we see real session sizes that make linear scanning painful.","tool_name":null,"tool_input":null,"source_record":{"timestamp":"2026-05-10T08:28:59.802Z","type":"response_item","payload":{"type":"message","role":"assistant","phase":"final_answer"}}}